* declared bin as an alias of binary
* changed the canonical name for the CP/M API format option to "cpm"
* implemented the --dump-decoding diagnostic command line option
* implemented a parser for decodings represented in text resources
* converted some of the previously hardcoded decodings (ascii, folded-ascii,
  latin-1, zx-spectrum) into text resources

== v0.1 2011-08-08

Initial release.
